# 🚀 Auto Price Dashboard

Modern web dashboard untuk mengelola produk, harga, dan stok.
Cocok untuk simulasi automation marketplace seperti Eldorado.gg.

---

## 📸 Preview

![Dashboard Preview](./Preview.png)

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

👉 https://auto-price-dashboard.vercel.app/

---

## ✨ Features

### 💼 Core Features

* 📦 Add / Delete Product
* 💰 Dynamic Pricing (No Limit)
* 📊 Dashboard Summary
* 🔍 Live Search
* 🔄 Toggle Active / Pause

---

### ⚡ UI / UX

* 🎨 Clean Dark UI
* 📱 Responsive Mobile
* ✨ Smooth Animation
* ⚡ Fast & Lightweight

---

### 🧠 System

* 💾 Local Storage (Auto Save)
* ✔️ Validation Form
* 🔢 Free Input Number

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript (Vanilla)

---

## 🚀 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Mufti-code/auto-price-dashboard.git
cd auto-price-dashboard
```

Open:

```
index.html
```

